data.description: There is LUXURY in Englewood!  This spacious 4 bedroom 2bath has an additional 2 bonus bedrooms in the basement for home office, workout, guest rooms etc. Bring your creative ideas. New flooring throughout.  Total gut bathroom with ceramic tile and jacuzzi bathtub to give you the perfect spa experience.  New ceiling fans throughout (Some remote operation).  The kitchen is a total gut with newly decorated cabinets, butcher block countertop, nickel black splash for the perfect setting for creating meals. Also, a new boiler and hot water tank! Upstairs you will find 2 spacious bedrooms with a shared full bathroom.  The backyard is your personal oasis with a gigantic brand new (sealed) deck that's covered and permits natural light to shine though w/sliding patio door that has built in privacy blinds.  Spacious backyard also has a brand new wooden privacy fence (sealed) to enjoy your yard and entertain on full cement slab.  New  STAINLESS STEEL stove, fridge, dishwasher, range microwave  Brand new Security camera (night time color) system can stay for additional $3k.  Come see this beauty!
